tip.text: Lean and Green is pretty good - a bit sweeter than I like green drinks so my guess it's the pear they combine with the apple. I should have asked for more lemon and ginger (tip for someone else).
Orders the pancakes w/ bananas + walnuts. Wished walnuts were caramelized instead of just thrown on top. Bananas just on top too - not very well-incorporated together for $ . Pretty presto though...
Had low expectations bc of the bland decor & knew they'd rebranded a couple times. But we ordered the veggie pho, shredded tofu spring rolls + tofu curry. delicious, flavorful and large bowls.

tip.text: Disappointed after expectations from reviews - came in winter and breakfast was boring. Orange juice was spoiled. Sure, try the Navajo fry bread if you have to...
